        "message": "Zoho OAuth2 client secret detected. This client secret is a confidential credential used to authenticate your application with Zoho's OAuth2 service. Exposing client secrets allows attackers to impersonate your application, request OAuth2 tokens on behalf of users, and gain unauthorized access to Zoho CRM data, email accounts, financial records in Zoho Books, and other sensitive business information. Immediately revoke this secret from your Zoho API console and implement secure credential storage with proper rotation policies.",
